#				  ${DISTDIR} (see below).  Also they will be fetched in this
#				  subdirectory from FreeBSD mirror sites.
# ALLFILES		- All of ${DISTFILES} and ${PATCHFILES}.
# NOFETCHFILES	- If set, don't download these files from the ${MASTER_SITES}
